  "title": "Inside Sales Executive",
  "description": "<h2><strong>Inside Sales Executive</strong></h2>\n<p>📍 Singapore | 💼 Full-Time | 💰 Basic + Incentives</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We are looking for a driven and confident <strong>Inside Sales Executive</strong> to join our growing team. This role is perfect for individuals who enjoy connecting with people, building relationships, and driving sales opportunities. No extensive experience is required — just a proactive mindset and a willingness to learn.</p>\n<h3><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Conduct outbound calls, emails, and follow-ups to generate new leads</li>\n  <li>Research and identify potential customers and market opportunities</li>\n  <li>Qualify leads and pass them to the sales team for conversion</li>\n  <li>Maintain accurate customer information and lead status in the CRM system</li>\n  <li>Build rapport with prospects through engaging and professional communication</li>\n  <li>Assist in scheduling meetings or product demos for the sales team</li>\n  <li>Collaborate with marketing and sales teams to improve lead quality and conversion rates</li>\n  <li>Track and report on lead generation activities and KPIs</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>Requirements</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in Business, Marketing, Communications, or related fields</li>\n  <li>At least 1 year of experience in inside sales, telemarketing, or lead generation (open to candidates with no experience but a strong interest in sales)</li>\n  <li>Excellent communication and interpersonal skills</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated, goal-driven, and resilient in a fast-paced environment</li>\n  <li>Comfortable using CRM tools and Microsoft Office Suite</li>\n</ul>\n<h3><strong>What’s in It for You</strong></h3>\n<ul>\n  <li>Competitive basic salary + attractive incentives</li>\n  <li>Structured training and career development</li>\n  <li>Supportive and collaborative team environment</li>\n  <li>Opportunity to gain valuable experience in sales and business development</li>\n</ul>\n<p>📩 Apply today and kick-start your career in sales!</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>WeCruit Pte Ltd</strong> | EA License No. <strong>20C0270</strong><br>\nEA Personnel: <strong>Tan Soon Hock (Steven)</strong> | Registration No. <strong>R1109889</strong></p>",
